OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBlustery
OL,6,Fshowers will clear from the east
OL,7,Fduring the evening. Dry overnight with
OL,8,Fincreasing clear periods and winds
OL,9,Ffalling light will bring a patchy
OL,10,Finland frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FThe morning will begin dry
OL,13,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Cloud and
OL,14,Fscattered showers will develop from
OL,15,Flate morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
