OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain, heavy at times, spread
OL,7,Fnortheast through Tuesday morning
OL,8,Fcontinuing through Tuesday night. This
OL,9,Frain turns clears Wednesday morning,
OL,10,Ffollowed by sunny spells and showers,
OL,11,Fcontinuing through Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
